<p>We have a solid foundation that comes with over 20 years selling our products to stores such as Macy&rsquo;s, Zale&rsquo;s Jewelry including eBay and Amazon. The same products that you can now buy from eOction at a wholesale cost and save even more through our ecommerce platforms. Our purpose is to always keep our customers in mind and deliver what you want, when you want at the best price.</p>
<p>We are based in Houston, with offices and warehouses in Mexico, India and China.</p>